      <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.25rem);font-weight:400;color:#f0ece4;line-height:1.12;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        Property Maintenance During a Brisbane Sale Campaign: Keeping Presentation Consistent from Launch to Settlement
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        The property has to look the same at the pre-settlement inspection as it did in the marketing photos. That sounds simple. Across a six week campaign in a Brisbane summer, with lawns growing, storms passing through, and open homes every weekend, it is anything but.
      </p>
    </div>
